data.description: Make this Retreat floorplan by RTS your new retreat! This move in ready, like new home, is awaiting its' new owners. As you enter you're greeted with a gorgeous two-story foyer. You will also find a formal dining room and an office/flex space. The large great room is equipped with an electric fireplace and  a view into the open concept kitchen which features an island and two pantries. A bedroom with access to a full bathroom is also found on the main floor. Upstairs, the owners suite has plenty of space and offers a private sitting area, spacious ensuite, and two walk in closets. Three additional bedrooms, a hall bath, and the laundry room complete this beautiful home. Don't forget to explore the .50 acre, fully fenced backyard and covered patio. Schedule a showing today!
